pageContext.claim: “Best Jobs Numbers in the history of our great Country! Many other things likewise. So why wouldn’t we win the Midterms? Dems can never do even nearly as well! Think of what will happen to your now beautiful 401-k’s!”
pageContext.analysis: The economy is doing well but Trump is wrong to claim the "best jobs numbers" in U.S. history. There have been many months with a lower unemployment rate.
